The next-generation PMAG 30 GEN M3 Window is a 30-round 5.56x45 NATO (.223 Remington) polymer magazine for AR15/M4 compatible weapons that features transparent windows to allow rapid visual identification of approximate number of rounds remaining. The new, easy to disassemble flared floorplate aids extraction and handling of the magazine while providing improved drop protection, but is slightly slimmer than before for better compatibility with tight double and triple magazine pouches.

 Durable dual-side transparent windows allow for quick determination of approximate number of rounds remaining in the magazine. postcontent:
This is a custom gun made by Benny Hill at Triangle Shooting Sports. Search the net and you will see he a famous for making outstanding firearms. I purchased this gun about 4 months ago but decided to focus on limited this year. So instead of it sitting around in a safe I thought I would give someone else the opportunity to shoot it like it deserves. I had this gun sighted in at 50 yards and “WOW”! It also has a VS trigger shoe so you can quickly change to whatever trigger you like without making trigger adjustments. Hard Chromed to minimize wear and keep it looking beautiful.
